natcurric:contentdescriptor-using-new-vocabulary-grammatical-constructions
  a skos:Concept, curric:ContentDescriptor ;
  skos:prefLabel """Drawing on new vocabulary and grammatical constructions from their reading and 
  listening, and using these consciously in their writing and speech to achieve particular 
